                                            <ol> <h3 class="title">Notas</h3> <li class="footnote " id="footnote1-09691_002_035"><a name="-09691_002_035">&nbsp;</a>
					<span class="label"><a name="footnote1-09691_002_035">1.</a></span>
					<p class="">La Estaca Mosc&uacute;, Rusia, se cre&oacute; el domingo 5 de junio de 2011.</p>
				</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote2-09691_002_035"><a name="-09691_002_035">&nbsp;</a>
