				</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote12-09691_002_035"><a name="-09691_002_035">&nbsp;</a>
					<span class="label"><a name="footnote12-09691_002_035">12.</a></span>
					<p class=""><a href="https://www.lds.org/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/20.26?lang=spa#25" target="_blank">3&nbsp;Nefi 20:26</a>.</p>
				</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote13-09691_002_035"><a name="-09691_002_035">&nbsp;</a>
					<span class="label"><a name="footnote13-09691_002_035">13.</a></span>
					<p class="">V&eacute;ase <a href="https://www.lds.org/scriptures/ot/gen/17.1-10,19?lang=spa#0" target="_blank">G&eacute;nesis 17:1&ndash;10, 19</a>; <a href="https://www.lds.org/scriptures/ot/lev/26.42?lang=spa#41" target="_blank">Lev&iacute;tico 26:42</a>; <a href="https://www.lds.org/scriptures/nt/acts/3.25?lang=spa#24" target="_blank">Hechos 3:25</a>; Gu&iacute;a para el estudio de la Escrituras: &ldquo;Abraham, convenio de&rdquo;.</p>
